name: Youmenkiden
summary: A sidescrolling action platformer in the style of NESFamicom games Play as high school student Zankirou Tougi as he is whisked away into a world where he must do battle against fearsome youkai

name: Disconcerting Unease 2
summary: Four small to mediumsized spooky Halloween maps an arctic outpost a Q2textured mining complex a pumpkin spice latte franchise place and an infinite horde arena Comes with a few new features a custom skybox and new sounds

name: All the Wiser
summary: A collection of birthday maps Major Arlene made last year for various members of the Doom community who are considered to be great influences and friends

name: You are Grounded!
summary: Its 1997 Haddonfield Illinois You are trapped in the basement Father is upstairs He has been drinking all day He wants to come down to give you a lesson Do you have the guts to survive

name: Candles of the Damned
summary: Remake of E1M2 from Quake a mediumsized medieval castle with many candles The map was previously released as part of Halloween Jam 2 Among other things this version features even more candles Comes with a new bat model and some ambient sounds

name: Brick Red
summary: Mediumsized terracottared brick castle based on the Progs_dump mod included Comes with a custom skybox and a few new soundsmodels The map and QC sources are included
There is no information on the last entry of CHAIN

name: Abraxas
summary: Link 19 in Haunted PS1s CHAIN is purported to mirror an unknown apocalypseesque event and its cover art supposedly has an intoxicating effect on some who witness it  Now there is nothing more to do I must do what I promised my father

name: Scary Library
summary: CHAIN link 18 revolves around a librarian in her workplace during a torrential thunderstorm The specimen can purportedly possess people

name: Vale
summary: Link 17 In a unique departure from most other case reports this one is entirely in Japanese and its subject follows an unknown protagonist in a dark forest
Appropriately titled 16 this CHAIN link may or may not be linked to an incident of occult Welsh origin

name: Specimen 15
summary: Mysterious disembodied eyes chase you in this link of Haunted PS1s CHAIN

name: Specimen #14
summary: Yet another untitled entry in Haunted PS1s CHAIN it follows an unknown protagonist hounded by mysterious eyeballlike creatures

name: Column Dodger
summary: For the 13th link in Haunted PS1s CHAIN is a simple dodging game Nearby metal objects are purported to migrate by a couple inches if the game is left on for a certain duration

name: Avert Your Eyes
summary: Link 12 in the Haunted PS1 CHAIN is footage from a hiking trip in west Germany The video quality is abhorrent for what should be a modern phone and the device itself is caked in ashes

name: Day 11
summary: The 11th link in the Haunted PS1 CHAIN is extremely anomalous and is known to cause psychosis and paranoia among the staff who play it or otherwise come in contact with it They are typically then reported either missing or dead There is no known way to handle this game safely

name: Organ of Eden
summary: The tenth entry within Haunted PS1s CHAIN is preceded by a report of a parasitic mind virus and a biostratigraphic diagram A medical team surrounds the player as gore begins to pile around them

name: Swell
summary: Link 9 of Haunted PS1S CHAIN initially resembles a PSX disc but is revealed in the research log to be some form of potentially living creature What follows is only explainable on those terms

name: Specimen #08
summary: The untitled eighth game in the Haunted PS1 CHAIN takes place in an unknown bloodsoaked location The only new detail given on the research log is an ultrasound image of an unknown figure

name: Ball Out
summary: Link 7 in the Haunted PS1 CHAIN provides souls in balls for the player to rebirth The research log indicates that the physical properties of the disc may not be completely inert

name: Dream Aether
summary: Dive deeper and deeper into dreams in this short musical experience  This is link 6 in the Haunted PS1 CHAIN

name: Drip
summary: The fifth link in the Haunted PS1 CHAIN anthology is a lovecraftian arcade platformer under the water

name: Emerge
summary: The fourth link in the CHAIN anthology is a mysterious exploration game Its case report has a mysterious now dried liquid on top of a mostly illegible synopsis

name: The Participants
summary: The third game in the HauntedPS1 CHAIN anthology it documents a nightmarelike trawl through a surrealist underwater world

name: Ms. Blanch,
summary: The second game in the HauntedPS1 CHAIN anthology it follows the interactions of a Ms Blanch and a man who attempts to drive her into the ocean

name: Torch
summary: The first game in the HauntedPS1 CHAIN anthology it follows a young woman exploring a cave with not but a singular torch Its case report details a labyrinth of walls and pathways in Utah first recorded on the 25th of August 1997

name: Cold Front
summary: Cold Front is a 4 map wad for limit removing ports featuring snowy landscapes and Egyptian architecture

name: The Mapwich 2: The Mapwichening
summary: The Mapwich 2 is a collaborative megawad for Doom II first released on October 2020 A sequel to the previous years The Mapwich the project was led by Bridgeburner56 and was once again based around the idea of pairing up mappers for each of the levels in the set but also having the pairs be randomly chosen the result was contributions of 45 mappers for a total of 22 maps Unlike its predecessor Mapwich 2 is built with the OTEX texture pack by ukiro and integrates the gameplay changes of the Supercharge mod by Tango

name: Barbie Girl
summary: Barbie Girl is a single limitremoving complevel 2 doom strict map for DOOM 2 This was made in response to a Doomworld post that nobody should ever use a MIDI of the pop song Barbie Girl by Aqua in a Doom map
storyline: The UAC has been conducting experiments on demons again  Theyve lost contact with the base where they were conducting the tests  What a shock  Your job is to go in and clear out the base  Alas a failsafe means that the exit from the complex cannot be accessed until the full test regimen has been completed  So youre ALSO going to need to make sure the tests are done  Dont let the test subject die or your only way out is as chunky giblets

name: WonderfulWhims
summary: WonderfulWhims is a standalone mod for The Sims 4 that offers plenty of social relationship and pregnancy enhancements in the forms of Attractiveness Impressions Personality Archetypes Menstrual Cycle Birth Control and many more

name: Delicious Quest
summary: Delicious Quest is a game about a dog on his journey to find the Holy Roast Turkey Unfortunately this dog cant control himself and will require your help to go further in his epic quest

name: Witches X Warlocks: Lawrence's Route
summary: This optional DLC comes with 40 mini CG illustrations one additional romance route Lawrence and 5 additional CGs in stunning HD  Time to enhance the game with these eye candies and have a spooktacular Halloween with Witches x Warlocks

name: Lust Campus
summary: Lust Campus is a multiadventure graphic novel with an emphasis on eroticism and intimacy with with a diverse cast of complex characters with whom you can connect and meet and who evolve or not thanks to your decisions throughout the story In LC you will find a game with a femenine gaze an empathy driven storytelling
storyline: In this VN you will be Alice an architecture student who has just arrived in the big city to try to make her fathers dream come true but the adventure will lead her to experience things that she would never have thought Through her you will be able to see what it is like to survive life on campus with the love erotic discoveries and problems that this entails Will you be able to achieve your goals Or maybe along the way you will discover that your destination lies elsewhere

name: BlindJump
summary: Blind Jump is a simple actionadventure game featuring procedurally generated level maps collectible items fluid animation and meticulously designed color palettes Evan Bowman started the project in late 2015 while in college and resumed work on the code after a several year long hiatus during which he was teaching himself oil painting Originally developed for macOS the game was rebuilt from scratch during the 2020 pandemic with a new custom engine Blind Jump now compiles for various other platforms including Linux Windows Nintendo Gameboy Advance and Sony PlayStation Portable

name: Bikes and Girls
summary: This game is a classic puzzle game with several levels of difficulty and beautiful arts

name: Glasses and Girls
summary: This game is a classic puzzle game with several levels of difficulty and beautiful arts

name: Webkinz Next
summary: Build your family of pets in the home of your dreams while playing fun games and hanging out with friends

name: Don't Freeze
summary: The spiritual predecessor to that one game about going hungry Can you escape the forest before you go mad Hey I think this place looks familiar
storyline: Set in a forest where the player must escape before going mad Dont Freeze is a survival game by Neonalig The player must navigate the forest find the river and craft a bridge to escape But beware the forest is cruel and the player must keep their vitalities in check heat thirst and hunger The player can craft items by dropping them on each other and cutting items by hitting them with an axe The player must also keep their temperature in check stay hydrated by crafting empty cups and filling them with water at the river and escape before they starve Will you be able to survive and escape the forest

name: Junsei Yasaotoko Sweet & Bitter
summary: TyranoScript remake with 3 new heroes
storyline: A shoujo manga style romcom otome game You can play two different school settings Sweet and Bitter This is a short omnibus novel with each route about 15 minutes long

name: Deviant Anomalies
summary: Deviant Anomalies is an adult visual novel and investigator simulator It features High quality renders with fully animated lewd scenes and immersive gameplay Solve baffling cases recruit Supernatural Anomalies into your team and help them control their newfound powers The more uninhibited their minds are the more their powers grow
storyline: A mysterious snowstorm engulfs the city and changes your life forever Ever since the bizarre snowstorm reports of supernatural occurrences begin to surface and crime rates are rising at an exponential level Netherhelm is in chaos YOU fresh out of college and armed with a fancy degree in Criminal Psychology decide to join law enforcement as a rookie detective  With a deepseated obsession to unravel the mysteries of the snowstorm you solve case after case as you trudge along the strings of fate towards your final destiny

name: Montezuma's Revenge
summary: This is the official version of the 80s classic game Montezumas Revenge rebooted by the original developer Its the classic puzzle solving action adventure platformer you loved in your youth

name: Thy Flesh
summary: Suddenly you find yourself standing right next to your car Your head hurts and your ears ring The front of your car is almost wrapped around a tree and there is smoke coming from the engine You realize that you dont know what happened or where you are

name: The Banshee
summary: Its a dark dreary night being driven away from sleep by the sound of thunder and slashing rain until you are compelled out of bed due to some mysterious sounds

name: Smart Technology
summary: Its almost Halloween Youve been hired to housesit for the reclusive widow who lives on the outskirts of town Her home is outfitted with the latest tech and an impressive artificial intelligence named Agatha controls it all But something has gone wrong The AI considers you an intruder and will neutralize you at the first sign of perceived hostility  Tread carefully Survive the evening Outsmart the AI  Agatha is watching

name: Not All There
summary: After working overtime one evening you go to the underground parking lot to search for your car you notice its nowhere to be found The parking lot is completely empty except for one car driving around in circles A sinister feeling that something bad is going to happen overwhelms you as you continue to search for your car Will you make it out alive or should you have stayed at work

name: Mortal Shell: Rotten Autumn
summary: Something sinister has arrived in Fallgrim Possess the Rotten Autumn update and access 10 new shell shades a brand new photo mode a new mini quest and an alternative boss OST by Rotting Christ

name: Lilith's Hunger
summary: Three witches go to the house of the newcomer in town She serves them tea with a gentle smile bit as one of them takes a sip Bera hears a loud noise and sees one of her friends fall onto the ground

name: Luar
summary: Luar is a Yume Nikki and an AN EARTH2 fangame At the start of the game the player is given the choice of two characters to play as Corey or Doberman The goal of the game is to explore and collect Valuables Precioso that change the protagonists appearance andor give them new abilities as well as items known as Dream Pieces

name: Husk
summary: Youve just inherited the estate of your distant relative Dr Hague Shoal who disappeared nearly a century ago  His home has been abandoned for decades and the realestate company refuses to send any more appraisers They insist that you go and clear out the property yourself  Whats the big deal What happened to the appraisers And whats that scraping sound coming from the walls  Husk is a short atmospheric horror game taking you through the story of Dr Shoal as you uncover his past and the horror that awaits in his decrepit home

name: Wizard Recurse
summary: Save a wizard from a timeloop using their magic hat

name: Squid! Escape! Fight!
summary: Swim under the sea with this hungry cephalopod and meet the other marine dwellers in this straight forward arcade adventure

name: Telos Legacy
summary: Telos is a fast paced multiplayer Arena Shooter with advanced movement slow TTK and a varied arsenal
storyline: Set in the Saharan desert oxide is a closequarters map depicting an abandonned factory that has now been transformed into one of the TELOS GAMES premier arenas  Set in a rich Asian capial skyrise is an absolutely massive map where players jump from rooftop to rooftop and traverse buildings at an impressive height  A simulation used to train machines the robots controlled by the players while playing legacy is a mediumsized map focused on vertical movement via its unique JumpPads set around the map  Set in an abandonned warehouse in the skyrise tower warehouse has some of the tightest corners and actionpacked combat in the game

name: Black Eyes
summary: Black Eyes is a atmospheric VHS aesthetic styled horror title inspired by the urban legend of black eyed kids and inspired by the title Among The Sleep  A short horror game for the Halloween season made in a few days  One late evening you awake from a nightmare about a girl with black eyes suddenly reality shifts and contorts and you feel something sinister trying to get in your room You must now prevent whatever it is from trying to get in while also finding a way out of your room and help get to your sisters room before its too late

name: Liars Maze
summary: All I need is this spell of my own making one more time one more time one more time

name: Star Conflict: Plague doctor
summary: This pack includes Jericho interceptor Plague Doctor Jericho rank 13 Coating Easy target Decor Blades Special bonus for everyone who buys the bundle  Premium license for 30 days

name: Deep Rock Galactic: Roughneck Pack
summary: If you really want to rough it up the Roughneck Pack has you covered Spice up your look with four new sets of unique armor one per class new helmets and new Paintjobs This pack is squarely aimed at those that cant be bothered dressing up as a space marine and just want to get stuck into the hard work at hand Finally show off those figurative guns  as well as that choice selection of tattoos youve kept under wraps for so long   4 unique suits of Armor one for each Class   A Roughneck Armor Paintjob for all your other armors   A unique helmet in two variants   A new Roughneck Weapon Paintjob matching the heavyduty armors   New matching Paintjob for Bosco   New Paintjob for your Pickaxe

name: Forêt de Nuages
summary: A walking simulator in a handdrawn environment Meet plants with strong characters and respond to their incongruous requests  Please be careful where you step your actions are not without consequences

name: Lightforce Ninja
summary: Platformer with ragdoll physics 10 stages in 5 different themed regions Challenging puzzles
storyline: The synthetic planet EARTH II is in great danger A parasitic Cyber moon from outer space has infected the planet causing the environment to mutate These mutations will produce red matter for the cyber moon to consume until the whole planet is drained There is only one hope left The Lightforce Ninja  Exploiting a bug in the light system of earth II the Lightforce Ninja are capable of manipulating the nature of physics This allows them to build teleporters and hightech armor powered by their LIGHTFORCE AMULETS  SENSEI HAZUKI sends his best student on a mission to destroy the power core of the cyber moon to save the planet from certain death

name: When Day Breaks
summary: When Day Breaks is a short SOMA mod that aims to turn S D Lockes Proposal from the SCP Foundation Wiki into a playable story featuring the key events and some additional ones with my own interpretation on the environments
storyline: 6 billion casualties within the first day Yet some managed to survive A passenger once to be associated with the Foundation came across a distress signal Could this signal dictate the next step to make for a dark salvation or rather to drag him into the punishing light

name: The Necro-Nom-icon
summary: Follow the recipelike instructions of the NecroNomicon and perform rituals to make contact with the Ancient Ones Will it provide the answers you have been looking for A reason for those odd dreams Or will you succumb to madness first

name: Pigments
summary: Get pigment droplets dodge the deadly razor discs paint all tiles

name: Unakiri Action!: Kiritan-hou no Nazo
summary: This is a sidescrolling 2D action game in which Touhoku Kiritan and Otomachi Una do their best
storyline: Touhoku Kiritan and Otomachi Unachan run through the stage using special weapons

name: Honey Select 2: Libido DX
summary: The ultimate sex simulator is here Honey Select 2 Libido Deluxe is a love letter to making love Engage with highquality fullycustomizable characters in every imaginable situation From romantic candlelight sex to the most specific kinks Honey Select is sure to satisfy you
storyline: Intuition Thats what brought you down this seldomtraveled street to this massive nondescript building A sense that somehow this was your fateand a decision youd never ever regret As you pushed open the gilded doors you were startled to see someone standing just inside to greet you as if she had been expecting you all along This stunning woman with the mysterious twinkle in her eyes introduced herself as Fur your humble guide to this humble establishment  Welcome to Honey Select A private establishment serving only the most discerning customers A place where anyone can find anyone and dreams can become reality The patrons here all have one thing in common theyre looking for a partner and that partner can be you  There are all types here Some are here to find a lifelong partner someone to care for to share joys and sorrows Some well theyre looking to tap into their primal carnal natures and forget everything in the heat of passion Some are tricksters their joy found from wrapping people around their fingers and maybejust maybegiving them what they want  Anything is permitted here Anything is possible Because this This is a palace of libido and youre its newest customer

name: Rocket League: Season 1
summary: The Season 1 Series include more than a dozen new items from Rare and Very Rare Decals and Wheels like the Bodacious Octane Decal and Shortquarter Wheels to Black Market items like the Stipple Gait Decal and the extremely animated BuffySugo Goal Explosion

name: All @ Once
summary: ALL  ONCE is a twine based interactive novel Take the role of Wyatt Reynolds your average everyday black teen in the small lakecentered town of Primwood a town where the world is quiet and the mornings are hazed Where Devils walk the street with pockets full of spice This young man whose life blinked by without a second thought becomes something more when his mind takes on something new When the thoughts in his head arent his own and the reality of reading peoples minds comes into play

name: The Migrant
summary: Axion is an alien being who was exiled from his planet a long time ago  Regretful for his actions he now travels the universe in search of a new planet to live in peace  Will Axion find a new home or succumb to the dangers of the unknown planets

name: Club Suicide
summary: Club Suicide is an antiromanticism otome game developed by Morpath for PC There are 20 endings in this game and players choices throughout the game will alter the ending of the game
storyline: Just 7 days before their graduation ceremony as the spring breeze began to blow these boys wished to end their own lives  As if to escape from the strife of interpersonal relationships you became a truant before you knew it When you came back to school for the first time in a while an odd club recruitment poster caught your eye  The name of the club was Club Suicide  You didnt have especially strong reasons but somehow you had thoughts of wanting to die Half out of casual interest and half with serious intent you ended up taking a look at the club  From now within 7 days well completely sever our attachments to this world and end our own lives You were overcome by the five club members seriousness and became afraid of committing suicide quickly coming to think I want to live instead  At the same time it wasnt like you had the courage nor felt you were in a position to tell them actually I dont want to die knowing that these boys were seriously working towards ending their own lives  You carried this secret in your heart and these strange repulsive 7 days had begun 7 days of following the boys desires and dark sides as they headed towards their deaths

name: Quake: Halloween Jam 3
summary: A Third Halloween Jam was held on QuakeAddicted a community project featuring 13 levels  a start map of varying sizes and themes Most of the maps use custom textures The pack is based on the Arcane Dimensions mod included and comes with various custom content like models sounds skyboxes and music tracks Some of the map sources are included

name: Quake: Epochs of Enmity
summary: Epochs of Enmity EoE is an original Episode Pack for Quake a collection of 12 maps A group of reputable mappers has been gathered together to form a vanilla feel episode The goal was to create an unofficial 6th episode to follow Quakes unofficial 5th Dimension of the Past The focus was to design a series of various themed maps where Ranger is traveling through time to stop the evil that is tainting the time continuum Main maps had to include at least one quad stay within the range of 100 enemies more if multiple quads exist and not use external models or sounds however skyboxes colored lighting and the fog were okay Mappers for the episode include the following Bal Fairweather FifthElephant Greenwood JCR Jpal Markie Music Nolcoz Rhoq and ZungryWare Due to the use of the progs_dump mod some minor quality of life changes have been made Epochs of Enmity also includes an original soundtrack
storyline: In this episode Ranger is stranded in time he must find an exit and fight through the hordes of ShubNiggurath scattered across the eras to go back to his timeline

name: Quake: Dwell
summary: Quake Dwell is a modification for Quake that features Four Episodes of varied and unique themes and Four Custom Bosses one for each Episode Brand new monsters including many returning from other Quake worlds New weapons to hunt down and utilize A Complete Soundtrack by Alekswithak Support for up to 4 player coop

name: Mega Man X Online: Deathmatch
summary: Mega Man X Online Deathmatch is a Mega Man X Multiplayer Fan Game  Ever wonder what would happen if you could use all the crazy weapons and abilities from Mega Man X games directly against other players Find out in this actionpacked online experience Battle against other fellow Reploids for the most kills in multiplayer matches on the internet or locally with AI opponents

name: Evilmun
summary: Evilmune has over 20 levels Two characters a knight and a mage The power of the magician freeze the power of the knight strike Combine their abilities to complete levels

name: Peculiar Fables: The Werebed

name: Voxella
summary: Welcome to the world of Voxella Here we see a young Muigi plopped into the world with nothing to do but discover Complete quests for other people find treasures explore dark caves and mysterious factories unlock the secrets of the world and have a friendly conversation with a giant spider Because in the world of Voxella everything is a conversation topic if you try hard enough

name: Knights of the Round Torus
summary: Meteor launching team building arcade action Clear the roads and defend the citizens of a magical torus for as long as you can

name: Don't Look Down
summary: Can you complete the Rite of Passage platforming trial and overcome Mokis fear of heights Dont Look Down is a first person platforming game with an emphasis on player movement and speedrunning potential You play as a fantasy rabbithumanoid character named Moki Moki must complete a Rite of Passage trial to obtain their full wings as they progress to become an adultlike mature member of their worlds society This trial is a challenging platforming course which requires Moki to use their base skills along with the skills they obtain along the way to prove they are worthy of wielding a full set of wings

name: Coriander and the Fall of Orion
summary: A tiny 3D adventure game where you talk to others and cut down trees

name: Eyad and Hala
summary: A short visual novel about life in Hamburg Eyad and Hala are two Palestinians living in Wilhelmsburg They find unexpected support from an Irishrun café

name: What Goes Pumpkin the Night
summary: Ren is bored in a cafe waiting for zir girlfriend on Halloween Nothing could go wrong

name: Cyberhold
summary: In the year 2306 a massive meteor is set to collide with Earth wiping out life as we know it TYPHON an aeronautical mining project has been assigned to deter the meteor away from Earth but only to find out that its a vessel for cybernetic activity  Cyberhold is a turnbased first person dungeon crawler with very basic Soulsborne elements

name: Halloween Chronicles: Cursed Family - Collector's Edition
summary: Solve the mystery and defeat the evil vampire that has possessed your uncle and threatens the entire town
storyline: Your uncle invites you to visit him after a few years so you could meet his family and spend the spooky holiday with them And you are more than happy to go for a visit and spend time with him Your beloved uncle was always a little eccentric but you quickly find out that something sinister is happening to him Even his own family has no idea what is happening so you need to unite and get to the bottom of this mystery Something evil is looming over the whole town and your skill of puzzlesolving and deduction can help save everyone in this special spooky hiddenobject quest

name: Halloween Chronicles: Cursed Family
summary: Solve the mystery and defeat the evil vampire that has possessed your uncle and threatens the entire town
storyline: Your uncle invites you to visit him after a few years so you could meet his family and spend the spooky holiday with them And you are more than happy to go for a visit and spend time with him Your beloved uncle was always a little eccentric but you quickly find out that something sinister is happening to him Even his own family has no idea what is happening so you need to unite and get to the bottom of this mystery Something evil is looming over the whole town and your skill of puzzlesolving and deduction can help save everyone in this special spooky hiddenobject quest

summary: Air hockey but you control both players Keep the puck from touching bad stuff to rack up points

name: Dungeonblade: Haunted Kingdom
summary: A text adventure game where you explore a living dungeon defeating otherworldly beasts and avoiding deadly traps on a journey to discover the legendary Golden Coins and defeat the Necromancer

summary: Multiplayer Retro Asteroids

name: Me Myself & Die

summary: Butterfly Collector is a pointandclick adventure game inspired by escape rooms Myst and fantastical gardens Play as a captured butterfly hybrid looking for a way to heal her broken wings

summary: Welcome to Goodboi Park Help the park defenders defend it from bodybuilders with their swivelling chairs

name: Spolous Ex
summary: Save the galaxy Danioy from invasion of army corps Doscoponian

name: Simple FPS Aim Trainer
summary: An FPS Aim Trainer for fast and lightweight target practice with built in game sensitivity conversion and matching easily switch between popular games to match your mouse sensitivity

summary: The story background of Red Alert is set up on the real modern battlefield Various mysterious military organizations in the world appear one by one trying to unify the world through war As a military commander trained by the country In order to defeat The evil forces of other countries you establish your own military base and develop yourself to fight against them and also establish contacts with other commanders communicate information arrange troops and fight the enemy together

name: Paper Pilgrim: The Crystal Case
summary: You and your brother have another Detective Case to solve More and more citizens of the Crystal City are disappearing without a trace  Experience a strange Adventure and bring the truth to light Is the pickpocket party involved Or is it the king with his robotic police force And whats up with the cursed swamp  Get to the bottom of the case by solving tricky riddles gaining information from peculiar inhabitants and collecting various items throughout your journey that can open up new doors and ways for you to succeed in your quest

summary: Deep Dreams is a traditional Yume Nikki fangame You play as Mariana exploring her dream world and collecting Alters

summary: Things get a little spicy during the Nordic Apocalypse

summary: A tiny tactical RPG where you lead a team of animal medics that are trying to contain a virus outbreak in a hospital Sounds like another day at the job except that the bacteria are way way bigger than they expected

summary: Experience the spring as a bluebird Choose the material for your nest feast on natures bounty in the form of seeds berries and worms and participate in quintessential bird activities Most of all take care of your eggs to make sure they hatch safe and sound And remember dont give up

summary: Dream Wires is a collaborated English Yume Nikki fangame created by sniperbob and Madoreptilian in RPG Maker 2003 The game stars Shigeru

summary: Sharpen your mind by crunching numbers in a relaxing way  The Yin Yang is a concept of dualism There must be some darkness in the light and some light in the darkness Shaolin Sudoku borrows this idea and presents it in an aesthetic sudoku game It might just be the most beautiful Sudoku game It is an indie game made by an Indian developer

storyline: You come home from a long day at work to find your partner cooking dinner for you but something isnt quite right

summary: Missing

name: After School: A Vocaloid RPG
summary: After SchoolA Vocaloid RPG is a survivalhorror Vocaloid RPG experience created using RPG Maker VX Ace Playing as Oliver you find yourself in a Spirit World an alternate dimension hosted by a single corrupted spirit You meet new characters and help spirits along the way while keeping an eye out for the corrupted host spirit The player must help Oliver escape this world safely while navigating the dangers it throws his way  Heavy inspiration was taken from games such as End Roll and Ib while the initial inspiration to start this project was taken from the song Crushed Mary by MondaijiP
storyline: Oliver spends a lot of time wandering around the desolate side of town When a heavy downpour starts he stumbles upon a school hes never seen before

name: Totally planet
summary: This game is a planet simulation that plays in the style of Reins where you make choices that impact how things progressed Although saying that this is a much easier game in terms of difficulty

summary: Briana has been craving some time off all summer and finally with her shoot wrapped for hiatus she can relax at her summer cottage on the lake To really enjoy herself she even drags her female costars along for the ride

summary: Missing

name: Soul Union
summary: Psychological Fantasy  Shape the Heart and Mind
storyline: Soul Union takes place in a world of elves and magic It tells the story of a cynical magic weaver named Ilyon After volunteering to undergo an unknown ritual he awakes to find himself trapped in a manifestation of his own psyche his soul labyrinth Thankfully he is not alone as his teacher prepared a stranger to serve as his vassal Using power empathy and logic he must confront the deepest unknown parts of himself if he is to successfully escape

storyline: You are Cliff a brand new freelance cameraman for Paranormal Entities the 2 ghost investigation show on the Hunting and Outdoors Cable Network You have been hired to inspect the St Augustine Asylum for the Mentally Ill Go into this facility follow the producers instruction through radio earpiece keep your camera on and try to make contact with the spirits inside If nothing happens you will get 500 for your time If you manage to get some amazing footage of real paranormal activity on your camera you will get an additional 2500 bonus Are you ready to be a part of Paranormal Entities history

name: Dungeons of Clay
summary: Explore the everchanging dungeons in the surreal world made of clay Unlock the hidden secrets overcome the dangers defeat dreadful creatures and reap the treasures to acquire almighty power Dont forget to bring your patience because you will have to merge all your talents and skills if youre ever going to reach the depths of the dungeon Procedurally generated dungeons tons of items and guns dynamic threats unique skills and randomized path stops will guarantee that no playthrough is the same Dungeons of Clay is built on the idea of permadeath and challenge but ensuring to maintain the fun with permanent unlockables and progress that rewards your time and increases your chances with each death

name: Faithless Trilogy
summary: The hellish minions left to wander in the aftermath of Koraxs defeat during the battle of Cronos have now scattered across Parthoris looking for fresh meat and a new realm to call their own Beings of chaos roam freely causing disarray in the realm The citizens of Parthoris have barely had time to rebuild their lives in the wake of DSparils reign of chaos which was put to an end by a yetunidentified outsider  You are Corvus You have laid low for a while in the dockside town of Port Mercy and become aware of the situation almost immediately Portals open in every corner of the town legions of the damned pouring forth and slaughtering the populace Stepping out into the pouring rain you come to a scene of fresh blood dashed against the cobbles deep red tendrils of it snaking into the gutters and raging monsters bellowing vicious cries of revenge as the townsfolk meet a gruesome end  They smell your blood and close in on you Standing at the foot of the belltower you brandish your elvenwand and confront the desperate beasts as they converge upon you The gleam of its topaz gem sends chills of fear down their backs  Its you  the faithless one
storyline: Parthoris is ablaze  ravaged by an invasion of unholy beasts it was not prepared for The gulf between the oncedistant realms of Parthoris and Cronos has all but disappeared as dark portals continue to open across your homeland and vast hordes of the undead and their cohorts from beyond Hells Maw spill forth slaughtering mercilessly in their bid to find you and exact their vengeance upon the Faithless One  You have already brought ruin to the first major guardian in your way  the fearsome Iron Sentinel and its army of liches  but this has enraged your pursuers further You now face the treacherous labyrinthine grounds of the Iron Fortress  a sprawling breeding ground for unholy knights malevolent magicians and terrifying beasts pulled from the underworlds deepest recesses This vast mountaintop fort is steeped in a dark aura of demonic possession that now reaches far across the realm corrupting the earth and its citizens beneath Beyond this foul structure who even knows what lies  Questions flood your mind as you enter its unholy gates  who or what is the soulless evil opening these portals And why do you feel a cold sense of dread as if someone may be watching you from the shadows Perhaps an old foe Or a new evil from some other realm Could it somehow be both

name: Ms.Director

storyline: Ordinary youth Ordinary love  Which boy will you choose  Play as Nanami and choose between two handsome creatures Kaito or Junya Go on dates romance those creatures but be careful if you make the wrong choice it might give you a bad end Make all the right choices and you may be rewarded with a kiss from your beloved and a happily ever after

summary: Missing
storyline: In a small village on the edge of the island a young resident named James leaves in search of something And what is he looking for Hes trying to get to the mountain top before Halloween He received a letter claiming that if he goes there before Halloween begins he can bring his parents back from the dead Is the note correct Is it good or evil Whats really beyond the forest  The nights before Halloween starts are ticking away

name: Koihime Enbu RyoRaiRai Version 3
summary: The longawaited arcade version Koihime Enbu RyoRaiRai Version 3 is finally making its debuts on Steam  New Playable Character Jokō Kōmei and New Strategist Kakuka Hōkō have been added to version 3 and renewed the motion graphics of existing characters  The complicated system has also been reworked to improve the playability The improvement includes adding a button dash and reintegrating the Special Down system into the Hougeki Combo The challenger mode and training mode has also been readjusted for version 3  Get ready for the new kinds of epic battles youd expect when warlords of ancient China clash

name: Extortion
summary: Youre a computer engineer with a terrible secret Someone is blackmailing you and now you have to hack some servers and get secret files for him Would you succeed to achieve his missions or would you find him and revenge
storyline: In this interactive story youre playing a computer engineer on its console line interface You have access to a whole set of commands and servers to connect andor attack Youll be forced to attack servers gradually increasing security  Will you success to achieve all missions that will be given to you  Connect attack download files bait security break firewall and many other actions that can be possible  Or will you choose to achieve minimum number of missions to track and revenge from your blackmailer   This interactive story will let you make some choice but will you make the right   One way to know join the story

storyline: The main kingdom of Euritia world was attacked by powerful army of outlaws and renegades You are a soldier from royal army who survived a crushing battle in the enemy territory in hope of defending your home land That is the beginning of the struggle for survival and the search for a way to try to change the course of you life in an already destructive and longlasting war

summary: Competitive puzzle game that involves matching three or more blocks of the same color vertically

name: Ascent of Titan

storyline: The UAC base on Saturns largest moon has been invaded by hellspawn and whos sent over there to deal with it Yes its Doomguy again This time another demon leader has gathered hells forces and is threatening to use UACs technology against them
